-  Preferred installation prefix.
-``BLOSC_INCLUDEDIR``
-  Preferred include directory e.g. <prefix>/include
-``BLOSC_LIBRARYDIR``
-  Preferred library directory e.g. <prefix>/lib
-``SYSTEM_LIBRARY_PATHS``
-  Paths appended to all include and lib searches.
-
